title: [Health] Frontline healthcare workers say they are angry at being treated as 'COVID cannon fodder, not COVID heroes' after responding to the virus for nearly two years and working at full capacity, reveal the findings of new research

[Health] In A Meta-Analysis Of 29 Million People, Researchers At Peking University Determined That Two In Five People Infected With COVID-19 Are Asymptomatic. The Findings Are Reported In The Journal JAMA.
